org.fcrepo.kernel.observer

Class FedoraEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.kernel.observer.FedoraEvent

  • public class FedoraEvent
extends Object
    A very simple abstraction to prevent event-driven machinery downstream from the repository from relying directly on a JCR interface Event. Can represent either a single JCR event or several.
    Since:
    Feb 19, 2013
    Author:
    ajs6f
